metadata.name: Joie de Vivre
metadata.description:
Crash Test Labs will serve as a showcase for CTJR-inspired art featuring Joyrider customs and derivatives from artists around the globe. 

The first release from Crash Test Labs comes from legendary artist @PapaDjoFranck. Currently living in France and known for his VandalzCrew and Vanitas projects, Papa brings his street-style graffiti to the classic Joyrider silhouette for this Crash Test Labs Open Edition.

#oeSZN
